<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background: linear-gradient(to right, #8b5cf6, #7c3aed); color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; text-align: center; }
      .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
      .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none; }
      .info-box { background: white; border-left: 4px solid #8b5cf6; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
      .info-row { display: flex; margin-bottom: 10px; }
      .info-label { font-weight: bold; width: 150px; color: #6b7280; }
      .info-value { color: #111827; }
      .status-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; background: #ede9fe; color: #5b21b6; }
      .action-box { background: #f5f3ff; border: 1px solid #c4b5fd; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; text-align: center; }
      .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; margin: 5px; background: #8b5cf6; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; }
      .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🔔 Nouvelle demande de congé à valider</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Bonjour <%= @manager.first_name %>,</p>

      <p><strong><%= @employee.full_name %></strong> a soumis une nouvelle demande de congé qui nécessite votre validation.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Employé:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= @employee.full_name %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Email:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= @employee.email %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Type de congé:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= @leave_request.leave_type_label %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Date de début:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= l(@leave_request.start_date, format: :long) %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Date de fin:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= l(@leave_request.end_date, format: :long) %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Nombre de jours:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= @leave_request.total_days %> jour(s)</span>
        </div>
        <% if @leave_request.reason.present? %>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Motif:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= @leave_request.reason %></span>
        </div>
        <% end %>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Statut:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><span class="status-badge">En attente de validation</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="action-box">
        <p style="margin-top: 0; font-weight: bold;">Action requise</p>
        <p>Veuillez vous connecter à Easy-RH pour approuver ou refuser cette demande.</p>
        <% if defined?(admin_leave_requests_url) %>
        <a href="<%= admin_leave_requests_url %>" class="button">Voir la demande</a>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <p>L'employé sera notifié par email de votre décision.</p>

      <p>
        Cordialement,<br>
        <strong>L'équipe Easy-RH</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement, merci de ne pas y répondre.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= Date.current.year %> Easy-RH. Tous droits réservés.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
